2:06:17.460 --> 2:06:20.420
One to Seven. Give me a sit rep.
Faisil, do you copy?

2:06:21.840 --> 2:06:23.970
Seven here.
21st floor secure.

2:06:24.050 --> 2:06:27.720
About 12 faction members
on the 20th floor. No hostages there.

2:06:27.810 --> 2:06:29.890
- Where's Dana?
- She's on the roof.

2:06:29.970 --> 2:06:35.230
Okay, stay put.
Give me that address again.

2:06:39.230 --> 2:06:40.990
You shoot me, this'll fall!

2:06:43.570 --> 2:06:46.320
Stay where you are!
Stay where you are!

2:06:50.580 --> 2:06:53.410
- Give me the key!
- I'll drop it, I swear!

2:06:57.840 --> 2:07:00.130
Give me the key.

2:07:00.210 --> 2:07:03.470
Come on, child.
You don't want to die, do you?

2:07:05.760 --> 2:07:09.850
Give me the key
and you won't get hurt.

2:07:09.930 --> 2:07:12.060
I give you my word!

2:07:13.230 --> 2:07:15.390
No way, you wacko!

2:07:20.690 --> 2:07:23.150
Help me!

2:08:13.620 --> 2:08:15.710
Please don't come any closer!

2:08:18.540 --> 2:08:20.250
Help me! Help me!

2:08:20.380 --> 2:08:21.840
Somebody!

2:08:33.890 --> 2:08:35.600
Dana, jump down!

2:08:35.680 --> 2:08:37.140
Jump down!

2:08:37.730 --> 2:08:39.230
Dad?

2:08:47.860 --> 2:08:49.490
Help me!

2:09:24.940 --> 2:09:27.190
Daddy, come back!

2:09:32.030 --> 2:09:41.750
Daddy, get me down!

2:09:38.790 --> 2:09:40.870
Jump! Jump!

2:09:41.000 --> 2:09:42.630
Daddy will catch you!

2:09:42.710 --> 2:09:44.840
-Jump!
- I can't!

2:09:49.220 --> 2:09:50.340
Hold on!

2:10:00.060 --> 2:10:02.400
Don't you let me fall, please!

2:10:02.480 --> 2:10:04.480
- Daddy!
- I got you!

2:10:04.560 --> 2:10:05.690
I'm slipping!

2:10:10.320 --> 2:10:12.280
Help me!
I'm gonna fall!

2:10:18.790 --> 2:10:20.410
Hold my hand!

2:10:24.460 --> 2:10:26.790
Hold on tight, honey.

2:11:21.810 --> 2:11:23.890
He's behind you!

2:11:25.230 --> 2:11:28.650
Take this plane down, now!
I'll kill her!

2:11:28.730 --> 2:11:31.530
Take it down, now!

2:11:48.380 --> 2:11:50.500
My God, do something!

2:11:57.760 --> 2:11:59.720
You're fired.

2:12:45.680 --> 2:12:47.980
It's okay.

2:12:50.770 --> 2:12:52.770
Honey, it's over.

2:13:01.740 --> 2:13:03.370
Hi, pumpkin.

2:13:06.950 --> 2:13:09.000
Just seconds after the jet landed...

2:13:09.080 --> 2:13:12.790
the unidentified pilot was escorted
from the scene by Federal agents.

2:13:12.880 --> 2:13:16.050
Though it is unclear at this moment
which agency was responsible...

2:13:16.130 --> 2:13:18.550
for the operation which ended
the terrorist threat...

2:13:18.670 --> 2:13:20.680
so dramatically
early this morning...

2:13:20.760 --> 2:13:22.760
we've learned from Miami Police...

2:13:30.520 --> 2:13:33.150
Do it properly.

2:13:33.230 --> 2:13:37.650
One, two, three, four,
I declare a thumb war.

2:13:37.740 --> 2:13:40.820
Five, six, seven, eight,
try to keep your thumbs straight.

2:13:40.910 --> 2:13:42.700
Don't! Stop it!

2:13:42.780 --> 2:13:45.830
- Wait!
- I got you!

2:13:45.910 --> 2:13:48.830
Just listen.
Listen to the rules.

2:13:53.670 --> 2:13:57.050
- Hello?
- Boris and Doris?

2:13:57.130 --> 2:13:58.880
We're on.

2:14:00.720 --> 2:14:02.720
Yes? Go ahead.

2:14:30.330 --> 2:14:32.370
Colonel, how nice to see you again.

2:14:32.460 --> 2:14:34.790
Good evening.

2:14:34.880 --> 2:14:36.710
Who was that?

2:14:45.850 --> 2:14:48.470
What's the scoop, team?
You see your contact yet?

2:14:48.560 --> 2:14:51.890
Haven't seen him yet.

2:14:52.020 --> 2:14:54.730
But I see somebody
I'd like to say hello to.

2:14:54.810 --> 2:14:57.020
Let me pour you
some more champagne.

2:14:57.110 --> 2:14:59.400
I got to keep up the waiter bit.

2:14:59.530 --> 2:15:02.110
These stakeouts can be tricky.

2:15:02.190 --> 2:15:05.620
You never know when things might
explode into a life-or-death situation.

2:15:05.740 --> 2:15:09.080
If it gets rough, stay low until
it's over and I'll contact you later.

2:15:09.160 --> 2:15:13.620
- Maybe you should give me your...
- So, we meet again, Carlos.

2:15:17.130 --> 2:15:19.800
Honey, I'm just gonna
do him right here, okay?

2:15:19.880 --> 2:15:21.420
Go for it.

2:15:22.840 --> 2:15:24.510
Oh, God.

2:15:30.350 --> 2:15:32.350
Fear is not an option.

2:15:44.780 --> 2:15:46.110
Dance?

2:15:50.200 --> 2:15:51.990
- Tango.
- Here we go.

2:16:08.010 --> 2:16:10.430
Harry? Helen? Guys?

2:16:10.510 --> 2:16:13.020
Come on, now.
Let's not get distracted.

2:16:13.100 --> 2:16:15.140
We got some work to do.

2:16:21.270 --> 2:16:23.480
All right, guys.
Come on.

2:16:23.570 --> 2:16:27.570
You guys better get serious in there.
I'd be serious if I was in there.

2:16:29.780 --> 2:16:32.410
Don't ignore me, Harry.
That's rude.

2:16:35.830 --> 2:16:37.870
All right, guys.
Come on.

2:16:40.880 --> 2:16:43.590
National security, guys.
Come on. Life and death.

2:16:52.970 --> 2:16:55.270
Helen, I was always on your side.

2:16:55.350 --> 2:16:57.390
I was always there for you.

2:17:35.850 --> 2:17:39.390
You know what?
I'm sick of being in the van.

2:17:39.520 --> 2:17:42.060
You guys are gonna be
in the van next time.

2:17:42.150 --> 2:17:44.650
I been in the van for 15 years.
